Eligible ka sa Genius discount sa POUSADA ONDA CARIOCA! Para makatipid sa accommodation na ito, kailangan mo lang mag-sign in.

Set in Cabo Frio, POUSADA ONDA CARIOCA offers beachfront accommodation 500 metres from Foguete Beach and offers various facilities, such as a garden, a terrace and a bar. 3 km from Molded Depth's Beach and 3.4 km from Dunes Park, the inn provides a private beach area. The accommodation features a shared kitchen and free WiFi throughout the property. Every room includes a private bathroom, while certain rooms will provide you with a balcony and others also provide guests with a sea view. The units will provide guests with a fridge. You can play billiards at the inn, and the area is popular for cycling. Municipal Estadium Alair Correia is 4.7 km from POUSADA ONDA CARIOCA, while Surf Museum is 5.5 km away. The nearest airport is Cabo Frio International Airport, 7 km from the accommodation.

Gusto ng mga couple ang lokasyon — ni-rate nila ito na 8.7 para sa trip ng dalawang tao.

    Nagsisimula ito sa isang booking

    Sinusundan ng pagbiyahe

    Sinusundan ng pagbiyahe

    Kapag naglagi ang bisita sa property, sinusuri nila kung gaano katahimik ang kuwarto, gaano kasarap ang pagkain, gaano kabait ang mga staff, at iba pa.

  • 3

    At pagkatapos, ang review

    At pagkatapos, ang review
